<p class="summary">韩国统一部稍早确认了这一消息。朝鲜此举戏剧性地表明了对前者的不满，此前数周，朝鲜一直威胁要终结两国最近的缓和关系。</p>

</li>
        <li class=" " data-tb-region-item>
<h3 class="regularSummaryHeadline"><a target="_blank" href="/china/20200616/china-he-xiangjian-kidnap/" title="美的创始人何享健遭入室挟持">美的创始人何享健遭入室挟持</a></h3>
<h6 class="byline"> 艾莎, 曹莉 <span class="time">15:58</span> </h6>
<div class="thumbnail">
	  <a href="/china/20200616/china-he-xiangjian-kidnap/" title="美的创始人何享健遭入室挟持">
        <img class="img-lazyload" data-url="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2020/06/15/business/15china-tycoon-1/15china-tycoon-1-thumbLarge.jpg" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAQAAAC1HAwCAAAAC0lEQVR42mNkYAAAAAYAAjCB0C8AAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="2018年，家电品牌美的的创始人何享健。" width="75" height="75"/>
	</a>
</div>

<p class="summary">据中国媒体报道，嫌犯闯入家电大亨何享健的家中将其挟持，何享健之子成功逃脱并报警。警方称已抓获五名嫌疑人，涉事事主安全。</p>

</li>
        <li class=" " data-tb-region-item><h4 class="kicker">简报</h4>
<h3 class="regularSummaryHeadline"><a target="_blank" href="/morning-brief/20200616/beijing-coronavirus-us-lgbt-workers/" title="美高院裁定LGBT就业免遭歧视">美高院裁定LGBT就业免遭歧视</a></h3>
<h6 class="byline"> <span class="en_byline">EMILY CHAN</span>, <span class="en_byline">KONEY BAI</span> <span class="time">09:51</span> </h6>
