	</a>
</div>

<p class="summary">欧盟各国重开边境；奥斯卡颁奖典礼延期；巴基斯坦重新开放后出现10万新病例；美的集团创始人遭入室挟持……这里是今日要闻。</p>

</li>
        <li class=" " data-tb-region-item>
<h3 class="regularSummaryHeadline"><a target="_blank" href="/business/20200615/china-decoupling/" title="世界想戒中国之瘾？“脱钩”代价高昂">世界想戒中国之瘾？“脱钩”代价高昂</a></h3>
<h6 class="byline"> <span class="en_byline">DAMIEN CAVE</span>, <span class="en_byline">MOTOKO RICH</span>, <span class="en_byline">JACK EWING</span> <span class="time"></span> </h6>
<div class="thumbnail">
	  <a href="/business/20200615/china-decoupling/" title="“脱钩”不易，全球经济戒中国之瘾恐代价高昂">
